üéØ CCEE QUICK MEMORY POINTS
CIA Triad = Confidentiality, Integrity, Availability
Passive ‚Üí observe (hard to detect)
Active ‚Üí modify / disrupt
DoS ‚Üí Availability
Phishing ‚Üí Social Engineering
